===Etymology===
From {{etyl|frm}} ''[[paragraphe]]'' from {{etyl|la}} ''[[paragraphus]]'' "sign for start of a new section of discourse" from {{etyl|grc}} [[παράγραφος]] from [[παρά]] "beside" and [[γράφω]] "I write".

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun}}

# A passage in text that is about a different subject from the preceding text, marked by commencing on a new line, the first line sometimes being indented.

